<ul>
  <li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6599815/what-is-the-difference-between-a-shim-and-a-polyfill">What is the difference between a shim and a polyfill?</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://2ality.com/2011/12/shim-vs-polyfill.html">shim vs polyfill?</a></li>
</ul>

